{"tid":2482634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年嘅五一黃金周又就快到啦","createTime":"2021-04-10T07:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T03:46:04.000Z","uid":147226,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"601502f167007daa70aff989ef42e4c48ddd30cc","tid":2482634,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T07:06:21.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得上年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🖐️☝️ 黃金周<br />\n<br />\n今年繼續瘋狂幫襯黃店，要間間都好似阿布泰咁買爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我明大家每日已經幫襯黃店，但通常係講平時嘅日用品或者基本食飯，黃金周就係食豪啲買豪啲嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS: 預咗PR公司會放負咁回應話黃店買野食野唔等於抗爭，不過唔好意思，五一黃金周最大目的係要騎劫呢個日子，騎劫到成個字唔可以出現微博，騎劫到任何商家想再用五一黃金周來吸引自由行都會搞到被小粉紅批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩你地PR公司諗掂條稿點寫同點拆先覆呢個 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa038b6c9831497e018bf8636c86dd4822ef795","tid":2482634,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T08:36:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87674a2232cd55baccff6d9dad17a97cc54f97c6","tid":2482634,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9ea0cabfc505a9f65741b87f874128965520391","tid":2482634,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T12:01:43.000Z","msg":"黃店類型好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好淨係去出名果D<br />\n<br />\n之前位澳洲插畫師在手足去左間黃紋身店<br />\n<br />\n好多人都係唔同位置付出 希望大家都行多步 唔好淨係排名店"},{"pid":"2b49b3c999321ecccc2c71f01509bb39baa21ed9","tid":2482634,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-10T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6004d1f670cf0398df0e6491a3ca767add979d62","tid":2482634,"uid":147226,"like":0,"d